include /build/section.pug      
#section-container
  +section(
    'Use cases',
    'What kinds of pApps can I build?',
    'Incognito is a new blockchain ecosystem with privacy at its center. Shielded accounts and transactions mean new opportunities for financial transactions, customer rewards, games, contracts, and more. '
  ).card-container
    .container.card-wrapper
      .card
        .card-icon 
          img(src=require('@image/build/build_apps_finance.svg'))
        .card-title Finance
        .card-description Use Incognito to buy, sell, hodl and trade crypto assets privately and anonymously.
      .card
        .card-icon 
          img(src=require('@image/build/build_apps_rewards.svg'))
        .card-title Rewards
        .card-description Integrate Incognito with your POS or e-commerce store to reward customers with private, tradable tokens.
      .card
        .card-icon 
          img(src=require('@image/build/build_apps_games.svg'))
        .card-title Games
        .card-description Take your games to the next level with secret token balances and transactions. 
      .card
        .card-icon 
          img(src=require('@image/build/build_apps_digital_cash.svg'))
        .card-title Digital Cash
        .card-descriptionn Integrate private stablecoins to your payroll or e-commerce store. Give users the privacy and stability of physical cash with the borderless freedom of cryptocurrency.

  +section(
    '',
    'Get funding for your project.',
    'DAO Grants provide funding to developers to want to create new privacy apps (pApps). Anyone can apply, and applications are reviewed on a rolling basis.',
  ).funding-project-container
    .container.content
      .highlight We want to fund apps that..
      div
        ul.desc
          li.desc Increase the number of users and transactions on Incognito.
          li.desc Take special advantage of Incognitoâ€™s privacy features.
          li.desc Can be deployed quickly.
          li.desc Also, we really like open source projects.
      .button-container
        a(
          href='https://forms.gle/5bDMeCXKmMbTkrwSA'
          target='_blank'
          ga-tracking
          data-ga-event-category='button' 
          data-ga-event-action='click' 
          data-ga-event-label='Create apps/Submit application'
        )
          button Submit an Application


  +section(
    'Support',
    'How can we help you?',
    'Incognito is committed to supporting developers. Let us know what you need.',
    'Join our Developer group on <a href="https://t.me/incognitodev" target="_blank">Telegram</a> or email us at <a href="mailto:go@incognito.org">go@incognito.org</a>.',
    'Get 5 PRV for filling out completing the <a href="https://forms.gle/Sg3wafqeFhyPKKYr9">Incognito Ecosystem Survey</a>.'
  )

  +section(
    'Discover',
    'Incognito is open source.',
    'Incognito embraces a full-stack approach to decentralized privacy, reimagining technology at every layer. Every line of its code is freely available.',
    'Anyone can participate, everyone can join, no one can ever restrict or control Incognito. Incognito is and will always be 100% open-source.'
  ).funding-container.container
    .container
      a(
        href='https://github.com/incognitochain?tab=repositories' 
        target='_blank'
        ga-tracking
        data-ga-event-category='button' 
        data-ga-event-action='click' 
        data-ga-event-label='Create apps/Browse the code'
      )
        button Browse the code
      .subscribe-email-container
        .container
          h1.title Keep in touch.
          p.desc Join our community of developers and be the first to receive updates on the SDK and DAO funding programs.
          include /common/subscribe_form
          +subscribe_email('Be the first', 'create-app')